TextBody:
Hello Karoline,

My name is Josh, and I'm happy to help upgrade Netwrix Enterprise Auditor. As it sounds like you already know, the upgrade will require two meetings:

The first is a 45-minute pre-flight meeting to plan out what components need to be upgraded and gather reference screenshots and backup configuration files. We will not be making any changes during the pre-flight meeting. The second is a 90-minute upgrade meeting where we perform the actual upgrade.

You can use the following links to schedule with me; however, I am out on PTO all next week. I do have availability tomorrow and Friday, but if my availability doesn't align well with your timetable, please let me know, and I will assign this ticket to another engineer.  Please make sure the upgrade meeting is scheduled after the pre-flight meeting.

Pre-flight (45-minutes):
https://nwxcorp.my.salesforce-sites.com/cts?Id=57GgZwJM8xljxzN2SaypuZDFrv4MRwYbHxV5TcsjANQ-Z&MeetingID=ode0CTAY4b6cP772MSbPFnzjjOE0s0PCmdHer8NfRJ0-Z

Upgrade (90-minutes):
https://nwxcorp.my.salesforce-sites.com/cts?Id=gVMXRRoE1mYWCxx9xjQet1OKPesp2_i57K3JvwCIZqw-Z&MeetingID=XtL_FUYcUSo6gUlGvvkng_5m2OqeauLlGxgCxaYZM9k-Z


Please let me know if you have any questions or concerns.

Thank you,


Joshua Sexton
Technical Support Engineer Tier 1
____________________ ______
Cybersecurity That Works for You

6160 Warren Parkway, Suite 100, Frisco, TX 75034
www.netwrix.com

My name is Josh, and I'm happy to help upgrade Netwrix Enterprise Auditor. As it sounds like you already know, the upgrade will require two meetings:

The first is a 45-minute pre-flight meeting to plan out what components need to be upgraded and gather reference screenshots and backup configuration files.
